title: New Hampshire Primary Vote: McCain, Romney, Huckabee, Giulinai and Ron Paul, United States, 2008
name: New Hampshire Primary Vote: McCain, Romney, Huckabee, Giulinai and Ron Paul, United States, 2008
description: The map shows votes for various GOP candidates by town/city/place in New Hampshire 2008 Primary. The data is for more than 95% precincts reporting the results. Also included is a field that shows ratio of McCain to Romney votes and logs of each candidate's votes.
